              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The relative population of the two states can be",
                "extracted from the observed ratio of strengths if the",
                "branching ratios of the gamma-decay of the two states",
                "are known. The branching ratios suggested by Warburton",
                "and Alburger  (see below) for this doublet were used.",
                "Book: E.K.Warburton and D.E.Alburger, in Nuclear",
                "spin-parity assignments, ed. by N.B.Gove and",
                "R.L.Robinson (Academic Press, New York, 1966) p.114."
              ]
            }
          ],
